{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/blog/js-fundamentals","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h3>1. Hoisting</h3>\n<p>변수 및 함수 선언이 물리적으로 작성한 코드의 상단으로 옮겨지는 것처럼 보이지만 실제로는 그렇지 않다.</p>\n<p>변수 및 함수 선언은 컴파일 단계에서 메모리에 저장되지만, 코드에서 입력한 위치와 정확히 일치한 곳에 있다.</p>\n<p>예시 1.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// undefined 가 리턴된다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> num<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nnum <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시 2.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">num <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>num<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 5 가 리턴된다</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> num<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시 3.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token function\">myName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"홍길동\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">myName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">name</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"내 이름은 \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// \"내 이름은 홍길동\" 이 콘솔에 찍힌다.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시 4.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>permanent<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>temporary<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> permanent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"영구적인\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> temporary <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"일시적인\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 초기화 이전에 접근할 수 없다는 에러가 뜬다</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>2. Callstack</h3>\n<p>여러 함수들을 호출하는 자바스크립트 파일에서 해당 위치를 추적하는 곳을 위한 메커니즘이다.\n현재 어떤 함수가 동작하고있는 지, 그 함수 내에서 어떤 함수가 동작하는 지, 다음에 어떤 함수가 호출되어야하는 지 등을 제어한다.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/eea4a/callstack.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Callstack\"\n        title=\"Callstack\"\n        src=\"/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/4b190/callstack.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/e07e9/callstack.jpg 200w,\n/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/066f9/callstack.jpg 400w,\n/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/4b190/callstack.jpg 800w,\n/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/e5166/callstack.jpg 1200w,\n/static/55661fa1473fa9084538c208bce4fd44/eea4a/callstack.jpg 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>위 그림을 보면, main() 이라는 파일 전체를 관장하는 함수가 가장 먼저 돌아가고 printSquare(4) 함수가 그 다음 square(n) 이 그 다음 multiply(n, n) 이 마지막으로 돌게 된다.</p>\n<h3>3. Scope</h3>\n<p>변수를 접근 할 수 있나 없나를 판별해주는 것으로 외부 Scope 와 내부 Scope 가 있다.</p>\n<p>예시 1.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">exampleFunction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// x 는 example Function 안에서만 쓸 수 있다</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"내부에서 선언된 변수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"내부 함수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// 에러가 뜬다</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시 2.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> x <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"외부에서 선언된 변수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">exampleFunction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">exampleFunction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"내부 함수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"외부 함수\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>x<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>4. 즉시 실행 함수 표현(IIFE, Immediately Invoked Function Expression)</h3>\n<p>정의되자마자 즉시 실행되는 함수.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>이는 Self-Executing Anonymous Function 으로 알려진 디자인 패턴이고, 크게 두 부분으로 구성된다.</p>\n<p>첫번째는 괄호((), Grouping Operator)로 둘러싸인 익명함수다.</p>\n<p>이는 전역 스코프에 불필요한 변수를 추가해서 오염시키는 것을 방지할 수 있을 뿐 아니라 IIFE 내부안으로 다른 변수들이 접근하는 것을 막을 수 있는 방법이다.</p>\n<p>두 번째 부분은 즉시 실행 함수를 생성하는 괄호()다.</p>\n<p>이를 통해 자바스크립트는 함수를 즉시 해석해서 실행한다.</p>\n<p>예시 1.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"안녕하세요\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"안녕한다니까요\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// 콘솔에는 \"안녕하세요\" 와 \"안녕하다니까요\" 둘다 찍힌다.</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>예시 2.)</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> name <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"길동\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// name is undefined</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>끝!</p>","excerpt":"1. Hoisting 변수 및 함수 선언이 물리적으로 작성한 코드의 상단으로 옮겨지는 것처럼 보이지만 실제로는 그렇지 않다. 변수 및 함수 선언은 컴파일 단계에서 메모리에 저장되지만, 코드에서 입력한 위치와 정확히 일치한 곳에 있다. 예시 1.) 예시 2.) 예시 3.) 예시 4.)…","frontmatter":{"date":"12 February, 2020","path":"/blog/js-fundamentals","title":"JavaScript 기본으로 알아둬야 하는 것"},"fields":{"readingTime":{"text":"2 min read"}}}},"pageContext":{}}}